Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11月26日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16时37分在太平洋地区出现的D-1被击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方的损失为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜水艇一艘、飞机5架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件结束后5A级O.P.A.R.T.S被收回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17时，发现有O.P.A.R.T.S异常反应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在也未能阻止那种\N发光现象和石化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来必须出席委员会议了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是诸位责任的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是作为负责人的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，我们应把昨天击毁的Dolem的\N残骸提交给上面…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件东西是很有说服力的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能证明由TERRA使用5A会有多好的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此，\N现在不是参加委员会议的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，所谓政治就是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管功刀司令并不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了现在这个阶段\N好像5A已经和他同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个，他现在在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要一个能够采集他处于\N融合状态时数据的设备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名绫人，\N今天工作结束了，你下床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令，我把绫人君带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛，他们两个怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像小孩子赌气似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个男孩不是很可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨天的检验结果看，\N你的身体好像没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是说他很高兴你没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经决定了你的住处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…紫东大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你带他去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么绫人君，咱们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来他讨厌这里的每一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话，让我送他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，我不是这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们被将了一军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是次序问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥小姐，下面我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，你有时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有点事想拜托你，可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不爱说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，总比说废话好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听过MU的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一种优美的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有丝毫的冗繁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU？Churchwared写到过的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.77,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}James Churchward(1851-1936):\N美国作家，1931年出版《失落的大陆——MU》一书，MU大陆学说的支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是传说，但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每件事物都需要名字吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的医生真讨厌，\N如果我真的健康的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不需要每天接受检查了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，今天能回家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我来这里接你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是前扣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是根来彼方的海湾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根来彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.37,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}根来彼方：原文为“ニライ カナイ”，官方翻译为“根来彼方”\N日本西南诸岛传承着这样的传说，每年神都会从名叫\N“ニライ カナイ”的理想乡而来，带给人们丰收和幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲绳传说中的理想乡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.75,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}“ニライ カナイ”的意思就是“大海彼岸的理想乡”\N从语源学的角度来讲，“ニライ”是指“（我们所来的）根源之地”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然年轻但是倒是知道的不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前面的根来岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些为调查遗迹而建的\N人造结构建筑物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构成了海上试验城市——神至市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.34,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}神至市：原文カナイ市，官方翻译为神至市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，就是右边那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫做根来彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个有趣的双关语吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀司令的专机\N看来他会在关西地区工作一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你那在奈利亚遗迹的RahXephon\N不被那些讨厌的家伙打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:37.58,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}奈利亚（ネリヤ）遗迹：“ネリヤ”是“ニライ”的别称，因此得名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧，它是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定对功刀司令有不少误解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是功刀司令的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他看起来有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实，他非常有人情味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个院子里的树是樱树…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是岛上的名胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年春天我第一次被邀请…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美丽的樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是神名绫人君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，久远小姐，你的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是录有D-1咏叹调的碟片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在这里做音乐研究
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…她是你的夫人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子是我最好的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有我妹妹和我两个人住，\N什么时候你都可以来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人，要是也住在这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远小姐会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要带你去的住处比这里更好，我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我妹妹别看她那样，其实很怕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块肉还没烤熟吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生啤！一扎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就开始喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝的是乌龙茶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一扎生啤！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是军人，\N对任务有疑问的话找你们上司去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被不是自己上司的人利用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把那个男孩变成你的道具吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经被你诬陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你和那个工具的关系恶化，\N真的没什么办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许一个好女人比一个好人更容易成为他的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他的管理这么宽松行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的生理节律和精神状态\N正在加速这种石化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么必须先让他解开心结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使对他进行电击，\N也是不能让这种现象停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像给你准备了一些用得上的日用品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让边上的洞洞堵住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容所还有多远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想TERRA很重视你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这个岛不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是有很刺激的事件发生，\N而且空气新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼也很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的车要开上这个坡道码？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，不…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊，我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…你已经到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要住在她家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我家，是我叔叔家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔我会住在那里，\N你不要太高兴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么口气？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，你品味真差…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，两个年轻人，\N后面的事情你们自己安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特意买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里和东京
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你家很不一样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你暂时还不习惯\N就当去亲戚家玩，轻松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没去过亲戚家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到吃晚饭还有一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带绫人君到周围看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？我平时不是教你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个，你的叔叔平时都说些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要住我们家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很为难…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让人家觉得因为和我吵架你才离开的好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会很为难的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘！弹珠汽水！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这里的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，请用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，你的手帕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和我那么亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，姐姐和我们一起住，\N你别想偷袭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，那个不去上学的女孩在约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不上学？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你有时候在军队工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过不要你的手帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那也没关系…\N至少你现在还有容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是摄影师？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，画家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢，\N一个想成为画家的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？这么说在Tokyo Jupiter里也有高中吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我也没什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只顾自己一个人喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，不过那个好喝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道弹珠汽水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道，但是没喝过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小球堵着根本喝不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，要把小球移到凹坑里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西谁会穿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔菲来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是你家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，等等，要吐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑哪儿去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宝贝！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说小惠的姐姐是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生啤！来一扎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是老板娘啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢，鱼很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月博士跟我说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根来彼方是一个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的小男生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天还说他是无聊的男孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要“锁定”姐姐我吗？“锁定”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让我们“缠斗”到明天早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“缠斗”！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君，能过来一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事要麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…六道先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我叔叔就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你经常教导小惠是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“己所不欲，勿施于人”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让她常记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个挂在门口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个，叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几点？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找小惠是找对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，一点问题也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我们会照顾他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我梳头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们常说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花那样红是因为树下埋着尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吸取了尸体的血液\N樱花才如此鲜艳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀司令院子里的樱花\N绽放出的鲜艳的蓝色难以言喻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道在那院子里埋着什么人？

Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱的极光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦涩的回忆,从记忆深处浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon第六乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭都市
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界饱含着声音


